Package de.tuberlin.dima.bdapro.dataIntegration.sensor.workflows

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SensorFeatureTableGeneration
    Flink workflow that creates the feature table for the sensor data by filtering and aggregating the sensor data.
    SensorFeatureTableGenerationTest
    Test cases for the SensorFiltering
    SensorFiltering
    Flink workflow that filters the sensor data to only include data of sensors whose closest weather station is contained in the downloaded weather data.
    SensorFilteringTest
    Test cases for the SensorFiltering
    SensorStatistics
    Flink workflow that calculates aggregated statistics from the sensor data that can be used for data exploration and matching sensor locations with weather stations.
    SensorStatisticsTest
    Test cases for the SensorStatistics, also tests UnifiedSensorWorkflow functionality.
    UnifiedSensorWorkflow
    Base class for Flink workflows loading sensor data from disk.
